entries.journal_entry_description: Do Vance Groten a favor and get his ring back.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: While Vance is working on fixing the beacon, he has asked a favor of you. Go speak with Herman Pate and retrieve a ring that Vance used as a marker in a game of sabacc. Vance has since paid off the marker, but Herman has yet to return the ring.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Vance's ring is in the possession of the leader of some local spice smugglers. You'll need to fight your way to the leader, Janelle.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Defeat Janelle of the mountaintop smugglers and retrieve Vance's ring.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Defeat Janelle and Get Vance's Ring
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return to Vance Groten with his ring
